  <description>
    <p>BeamerPresenter shows a PDF presentation to speaker and audience in a
    multi-screen setup with various control options and extra information
    for the speaker.</p>
    <p>Features:
    <ul>
      <li>draw, highlight and point on the presentation with tools selected per input device</li>
      <li>supports pressure sensitive stylus input and different draw styles (e.g. Wacom tablet)</li>
      <li>save drawings in format compatible with Xournal++</li>
      <li>videos and sounds linked from a PDF file</li>
      <li>slide transitions and basic animations</li>
      <li>fast slide changes and browsing due to compressed cache of slides (configurable cache size)</li>
      <li>modular, configurable user interface for maximal flexibility</li>
      <li>does not try to take the role of your window manager</li>
    </ul>
    </p>
  </description>
